			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Rose Whitmore</span></strong>&rsquo;s work has appeared in the <em>Missouri Review</em> and <em>Mason&rsquo;s Road</em>. Before earning her <span class="smallcaps">MFA</span>, she played for the U.S. Women&rsquo;s National Rugby Team, walked across Spain, and worked for <em>Prishtina Insight</em>, an English-language newspaper in Kosovo. She lives in the San Francisco Bay Area.</p><a href="/contributors/rose-whitmore" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
