					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li><a href="/issues/317">May 2002</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


														<a href="/issues/317" class="block-content-photo cover-thumb">
					
